\v 4 Que tendes vós comigo, <a name="02900400400012" ll="SDBH:צֹר:001000" il="pcm02741">Tiro</a>, e <a name="02900400400016" ll="SDBH:צִידֹון:000001" il="Bolen00097;HK00372;adr090508677;adr1307138853;pcm02737">Sidom</a>, e todas as <a name="02900400400022" ll="SDBH:גְּלִילָה:000000">regiões</a> da <a name="02900400400024" ll="SDBH:פְּלֶשֶׁת:000000" il="adr0807102851">Filístia</a>? É isso <a name="02900400400028" ll="SDBH:גְּמוּל:000001">vingança</a> que <a name="02900400400032" ll="SDBH:שׁלם:000007">quereis</a> contra mim? Se assim me <a name="02900400400040" ll="SDBH:גמל:001000">quereis</a> <a name="02900400400040" ll="SDBH:גמל:001000">vingar</a>, <a name="02900400400050" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000032">farei</a>, <a name="02900400400046;02900400400048" ll="SDBH:מְהֵרָה:000000;SDBH:קַל:000001">sem</a> <a name="02900400400046;02900400400048" ll="SDBH:מְהֵרָה:000000;SDBH:קַל:000001">demora</a>, <a name="02900400400050" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000032">cair</a> sobre a <a name="02900400400056" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">vossa</a> <a name="02900400400056" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">cabeça</a> a <a name="02900400400052" ll="SDBH:גְּמוּל:000000">vossa</a> <a name="02900400400052" ll="SDBH:גְּמוּל:000000">vingança</a>. 
